Class AlloppMulLabTree

java.lang.Object
  dr.evomodel.speciation.AlloppMulLabTree

public class AlloppMulLabTree
extends java.lang.Object

An AlloppMulLabTree represents the species network as single binary tree with tips that can be multiply labelled with species.

Graham Jones Date: 13/09/2011
